Crypt-ProtectedString version 0.00_01
=====================================

This module is still in very, very early development.  It is by no means stable
or production ready!  Please read the documentation provided inside the module 
code (POD) for the disclaimer and copyright/license information.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Module::Pluggable
  Digest::SHA1
  Crypt::RSA
  Crypt::RSA::Key::Public
  Crypt::RSA::Key::Private
  Carp (not yet used)

...maybe others.  I'll update the list when I have time for further development.


